      Users want well written comments
          o

            Flesch-Kincaid Readability (comprehension difficulty)
          o

            Gunning-Fog Index (writing grade level estimate)
          o

            Average sentence length ^
          o

            Number of words in comment ^
            Number of characters in comment ^
            Average syllable ^
    *

      Users want novel discussion
          o

            Frequent word index (how often the comment uses words that are frequent in comments generally
          o

            Number of sub-comments ^
